Instructions for the compilation of this document
-------------------------------------------------

1. Clone the ``tesis`` repository (probably you already have).

2. Clone also ``usmtesis``.

3. Edit the ``url`` attribute in ``tesis/.gitmodules``
   to point to the path where you cloned ``usmtesis``.

4. Initialize usmtesis within tesis::

    cd tesis
    git submodule update --init

5. Compile the images in usmtesis::

    cd memoria/usmtesis/images
    make

6. Compile the document::

    cd ../../
    make

